      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "It's natural to feel overwhelmed by the challenges you're facing, especially when it comes to the well-being of your loved ones. The love you express for them is evident, but it's also important to recognize that your well-being is just as crucial. Sometimes, letting go isn't about giving up on yourself, but rather finding a way to live more independently and reduce the strain on your family. It might be helpful to explore options for assistance, whether it's through community resources, support groups, or professional help. Remember, seeking help doesn't make you selfish; it shows strength and a desire to improve your situation for everyone's benefit.",
